These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
Food: mango, pepper, pomegranate, raspberry
City: hannover, rome, new-york, boston
1. City:rome is on the left of City:hannover##1
2. Food:mango == City:boston##1
3. City:new-york is on the right of City:hannover##1
4. Food:pepper is on the left of City:boston##1
5. Food:raspberry is on the left of City:hannover##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | raspberry | pomegranate | pepper | mango   |
| City   | rome  | hannover     | new-york   | boston |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
Hobby: camping, cooking, video-games, woodworking
City: hannover, rome, nizza, berlin
1. Hobby:woodworking == City:rome##1
2. Hobby:camping is on the far right##1
3. Hobby:cooking is on the right of Hobby:woodworking##1
4. Hobby:woodworking is on the right of City:nizza##1
5. City:rome is on the left of City:hannover##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby   | video-games | woodworking | cooking | camping    |
| City   | nizza    | rome      | hannover | berlin |

