2. Music-Genre:r&b is on the right of Music-Genre:disco##1
3. City:prague is on the right of City:liverpool##1
4. City:berlin is on the far left##1
5. City:rome == Music-Genre:disco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |       3       |   4   |
| City      | berlin | rome  | liverpool | prague |
| Music-Genre   | blues  | disco | r&b           | d&b   |

