.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-20::.
Nationality: american, argentine, mexican, nigerian
Flower: iris, daffodil, bellflower, daisy
1. Flower:iris is on the left of Nationality:argentine##1
2. Flower:daffodil is on the left of Nationality:nigerian##1
3. Nationality:american is on the left of Nationality:mexican##1
4. Nationality:nigerian == Flower:daisy##1
5. Flower:iris is on the left of Nationality:argentine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Nationality   | american | mexican | argentine | nigerian   |
| Flower     | bellflower  | iris    | daffodil       | daisy |

 